REAL COMPANY SCENARIOS YOU MUST KNOW
Scenario A: Deployment server CPU spike at midnight

Cause: Backup cron job running.

Fix:

Check cron:

crontab -l


Move heavy job to off-peak time.

Scenario B: Production server becoming slow randomly

Check:

vmstat 1 5
iostat -x 2


Root cause: I/O wait.

Scenario C: Application not starting

Check logs:

journalctl -u appname


Check memory:

free -h

Scenario D: DB process consuming high RAM

Temporary fix:

systemctl restart mariadb

Scenario E: Too many orphan processes

Fix: Restart parent service or reboot.
